Crush is a mobile app that allows users to match with their contacts.

18.description:
Crush is a mobile app that allows users to match with their contacts. The startup was founded in 2021 and is based in Barranquilla, Colombia. 

At some point everyone’s had a crush on a close friend or peer from college or university. We have their contact information, we meet and speak to them almost on a daily basis yet some of us are afraid to discuss our emotions towards them. Crush knows that for some people is very difficult to take the first step, we're afraid of ending friendzoned and exposed and can risk permanently damaging a beautiful friendship. Crush offers a practical and risk-free solution for people who struggle to take that first step. 

People can use Crush to send an anonymous message to their crush, and if they're reciprocrated (also anonymously) then Crush reveals it to both. Only when both persons have a mutual crush on themselves Crush reveals it to them so that they can go out on a date.

Our goal is to make it easier and risk-free to match with your crush that being someone you already hang out with as friends or peers.
